{"comments":"QR Encoding Mode — Character set and bit efficiency modes.\n\n## Modes\n\nDifferent modes have different character sets and bit efficiencies:\n- Numeric: 0-9 only, 10 bits per 3 digits\n- Alphanumeric: 0-9, A-Z, space, $%*+-./: — 11 bits per 2 chars\n- Byte: Any byte, 8 bits per character\n- Kanji: Shift-JIS double-byte, 13 bits per character\n- ECI: Extended Channel Interpretation (for other encodings)\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Prelude (Eq, Ord, Show)\n- Data.Char (character codes)\n- Data.Array (all)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[63,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Types/EncodingMode.purs","start":[63,3]},"title":"ModeNumeric"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[64,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Types/EncodingMode.purs","start":[64,3]},"title":"ModeAlphanumeric"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[65,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Types/EncodingMode.purs","start":[65,3]},"title":"ModeByte"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[66,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Types/EncodingMode.purs","start":[66,3]},"title":"ModeKanji"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[67,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Types/EncodingMode.purs","start":[67,3]},"title":"ModeECI"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","QRCode","Types","EncodingMode"],"EncodingMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":